[quest]Indistinct Tentacle[/quest]

§6Machine Type:§r Modularized Machine - §aAssembly Line§r | §aComponent Assembly Line§r | §aAssembler§r | §aPrecise Assembler§r

Place §9Modular Hatches§r around the controller to enhance your machine.

[note]The MK2 Tentacle is not expressly required to finish Twist, but if you want to spend the resources to get it, it will be fast[/note]

Glass Tier limits Energy Hatch Tier | Laser Hatches require UV+ Glass

Component Casing Tier limits Recipe Tier | Casing Tier requires at least recipe voltage level - §c1§r

If Component Casing Tier is higher than recipe tier, enable §9Perfect Overclock§r

UMV+ Glass and Component Casing enables §aWireless Mode§r

Processing Time is §bfixed§r in Wireless Mode.

§6Installable Modules§r are: 

§cParallel Controller Module§r: Sets machine parallels
§cPower Consumption Controller Module§r: Reduces machine energy consumption
§cExecution Core Module§r: Adds additional running units to machine, enabling §9True Parallelism§r

[warn]Only the §aPerfect Execution Core Module§r can be installed on the Tentacle MK2[/warn]

§6 --- Details --- §r

Default Speed:

Assembly Line: §c100%§r
Component Assembly Line: §c200%§r
Assembler: §c400%§r
Precise Assembler: §c400%§r

Default Parallel = §c256§r

In Wireless Mode, time is fixed at §c25.6§r seconds.

Using an §bAstral Array Fabricator§r in controller slot, processing time is fixed to §c1§r second, and EU cost increases to §c64x§r 

[note]Use a §aScrewdriver§r to change modes[/note]
